metadata.name: 300Gorillas: Cross River Gorilla #1
metadata.description: 300 Gorillas, 300 NFTs. A collection by the African Conservation Foundation to protect critically endangered Cross River Gorillas and their habitat. Cross River gorillas are the most endangered great ape on the planet. So rare that they were once thought to be extinct, but in 1983 they were rediscovered and currently around 300 are living in remote areas of Cameroon and Nigeria. Help us save these magnificent creatures.
